text: Wicked Lips is the fifth extended play by Australian rapper Iggy Azalea. It was released on December 2, 2019, by Bad Dream Records and Empire. == Track listing == == Personnel == * Iggy Azalea – lead vocals * Alice Chater – featured vocals * Pabllo Vittar – featured vocals == References == Category:2019 albums Category:Iggy Azalea Category:Rap music
title: Wicked Lips
